document_data.Notable Users:
* These were among the magical items commonly used by [[planewalker]]s and could be purchased in the markets of [[Sigil]] at prices lower than those on the [[Prime Material plane]].
* Powerful [[wizard]]s often had them as specimens of study within their laboratories.
* Dissolved ''air spores'' were one of the ingredients of the [[steel dragon]] [[Zundaerazylym]]'s magical mixture ''[[longbite]]''.{{Cite dragon/259/Wyrms of the North: Zundaerazylym|72}}
